[
    {
        "text": "It took 30,000 tons of snow and about 500 tons of ice...",
        "startTime": 19236,
        "endTime": 23498,
        "slowStartTime": 29004,
        "slowEndTime": 35472
    },
    {
        "text": "...to make the Ice Hotel in Quebec.",
        "startTime": 23592,
        "endTime": 25145,
        "slowStartTime": 35538,
        "slowEndTime": 37942
    },
    {
        "text": "These days, about 100,000 people a year will visit the hotel,...",
        "startTime": 25665,
        "endTime": 28799,
        "slowStartTime": 38647,
        "slowEndTime": 43424
    },
    {
        "text": "...but about 5,000 have the nerve to spend the entire night.",
        "startTime": 29162,
        "endTime": 33119,
        "slowStartTime": 43893,
        "slowEndTime": 49903
    },
    {
        "text": "You'll get complete instructions on what to wear...",
        "startTime": 33965,
        "endTime": 36486,
        "slowStartTime": 51097,
        "slowEndTime": 54954
    },
    {
        "text": "...and how to use the extra strength sleeping bag.",
        "startTime": 36585,
        "endTime": 38988,
        "slowStartTime": 55027,
        "slowEndTime": 58707
    },
    {
        "text": "A few common areas include crystalline halls, a slide, and a coffee shop.",
        "startTime": 39931,
        "endTime": 44724,
        "slowStartTime": 60046,
        "slowEndTime": 67311
    },
    {
        "text": "One of the most stunning aspects of the Ice Hotel is this chapel here.",
        "startTime": 45501,
        "endTime": 49516,
        "slowStartTime": 68402,
        "slowEndTime": 74499
    },
    {
        "text": "Some 40 couples got married here this year.",
        "startTime": 49833,
        "endTime": 52053,
        "slowStartTime": 74900,
        "slowEndTime": 78305
    },
    {
        "text": "Imagine the wardrobe.",
        "startTime": 52501,
        "endTime": 53789,
        "slowStartTime": 78901,
        "slowEndTime": 80908
    },
    {
        "text": "The place where everyone goes is to the Ice Bar,...",
        "startTime": 54639,
        "endTime": 57315,
        "slowStartTime": 82109,
        "slowEndTime": 86197
    },
    {
        "text": "...where unique beverages are served up in ice glasses.",
        "startTime": 57536,
        "endTime": 60392,
        "slowStartTime": 86454,
        "slowEndTime": 90813
    },
    {
        "text": "It's like being dropped onto the set of a science fiction movie...",
        "startTime": 60803,
        "endTime": 63859,
        "slowStartTime": 91355,
        "slowEndTime": 96013
    },
    {
        "text": "...and animated visitors are finding all sorts of ways to keep warm...",
        "startTime": 64097,
        "endTime": 68185,
        "slowStartTime": 96296,
        "slowEndTime": 102503
    },
    {
        "text": "...while enjoying the unique ambience.",
        "startTime": 68305,
        "endTime": 70318,
        "slowStartTime": 102607,
        "slowEndTime": 105702
    },
    {
        "text": "In the daytime, before the overnight guests check in,...",
        "startTime": 72735,
        "endTime": 75905,
        "slowStartTime": 109253,
        "slowEndTime": 114083
    },
    {
        "text": "...visitors can tour all of the rooms.",
        "startTime": 76048,
        "endTime": 78042,
        "slowStartTime": 114222,
        "slowEndTime": 117288
    },
    {
        "text": "Many of which are artistically carved along a special theme.",
        "startTime": 78233,
        "endTime": 81556,
        "slowStartTime": 117500,
        "slowEndTime": 122559
    },
    {
        "text": "One suite is like a crystal palace...",
        "startTime": 82265,
        "endTime": 84161,
        "slowStartTime": 123547,
        "slowEndTime": 126466
    },
    {
        "text": "...and another is called the mermaid room.",
        "startTime": 84370,
        "endTime": 86258,
        "slowStartTime": 126705,
        "slowEndTime": 129612
    },
    {
        "text": "All of the ice block beds are covered in a piece of faux fur...",
        "startTime": 87177,
        "endTime": 90451,
        "slowStartTime": 130916,
        "slowEndTime": 135901
    },
    {
        "text": "...and a colorful fiber-optic lighting creates a surreal touch.",
        "startTime": 90765,
        "endTime": 94053,
        "slowStartTime": 136298,
        "slowEndTime": 141305
    },
    {
        "text": "Open for three months of the year,...",
        "startTime": 95228,
        "endTime": 97085,
        "slowStartTime": 142992,
        "slowEndTime": 145852
    },
    {
        "text": "...the enigmatic Ice Hotel is about a forty-minute drive from Quebec City.",
        "startTime": 97376,
        "endTime": 101123,
        "slowStartTime": 146214,
        "slowEndTime": 151909
    },
    {
        "text": "For TravelVideo.tv, I'm Bea Broda.",
